description	"Sith Trooper Captain

^2Weaponry:
- Heavy Blaster Pistol (3)
- Repeating Blaster [T-21] (2)
- Stun Baton
-- Yellow / Cyan Styles

^8Attributes:
- Healing (2)
- Rally

^3Abilities:
- Dodge (2) ^3[CS1]
- Dash (2) ^3[CS2]

The Sith Troopers were infantry units in the armed forces of the Sith Empire during the Jedi Civil War. This captain commands the other sith troopers."